org.digijava.module.aim.action

Class GetActivities

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.struts.action.Action
      • org.digijava.module.aim.action.GetActivities

  • public class GetActivities
extends org.apache.struts.action.Action
    Returns XML of Activities list depending on request parameters. This action is called asynchronously from NPD, but can be used in any other place where Activity list is needed.
